column16: Alex Avila flies out to left fielder David Murphy in foul territory.
Don Kelly singles on a soft ground ball to third baseman Jurickson Profar.  Jhonny Peralta advances to 3rd, on a throwing error by third baseman Jurickson Profar.
Austin Jackson flies out to right fielder Nelson Cruz.
Ramon Santiago pops out to third baseman Adrian Beltre.
Andy Dirks flies out to left fielder Jurickson Profar in foul territory.
